## The generated No-Intro index: the server builds its own on first boot, so it is never committed.
nointro.db

## Art cache: originals and renders are transient, and the originals layer holds full-resolution
## covers we do not own; retention is capped at 7 days for that reason.
cache/
originals/
renders/

## Atomic-write temporaries. AtomicFile sweeps these at startup, but a hard kill can leave them.
*.tmp

